# 非原版代码新增逻辑, 排序按照字母顺序，新增忽略文件，都加在最头上，避免和原版社区的代码合并冲突
.cli-proxy-api
target

# Binaries
cli-proxy-api
*.exe

# Configuration
config.yaml
.env

# Generated content
bin/*
logs/*
conv/*
temp/*
refs/*

# Storage backends
pgstore/*
gitstore/*
objectstore/*

# Static assets
static/*

# Authentication data
auths/*
!auths/.gitkeep

# Documentation
docs/*
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
GEMINI.md

# Tooling metadata
.vscode/*
.worktrees/
.codex/*
.claude/*
.gemini/*
.serena/*
.agent/*
.agents/*
.opencode/*
.idea/*
.beads/*
.bmad/*
_bmad/*
_bmad-output/*

# macOS
.DS_Store
._*
.gocache/
